overview: Pak Bejo and Sutini are a poor family in a small village on a mountainside. The harvest of their rice fields fail and Sutini who sell fried snacks in the market also was not doing well with the selling. In the most difficult days of their life. There were many events was held in a village and due to the culture rules, everyone has to attend and donate money. The frustrated Mr. Bejo made a plan to be donated by villagers when he found himself in aÂ terrible economy moment.
title: Nyumbang
